	        C79,0.8,79.5,0.5,80,0.5V39.4z" />
                        <path class="helft" d="M80,0.5c0.5,0,0.9,0.2,1.2,0.7l0,0l6.4,15l16.3,1.4c1.1,0.1,1.6,1.5,0.7,2.2L92.2,30.5l3.7,15.9
